1 get the latest gtags install lib, from: https://ftp.gnu.org/pub/gnu/global/

2 install gtags dependency library
sudo apt build-dep global
sudo apt install libncurses5-dev libncursesw5-dev

3 download the gtags: https://ftp.gnu.org/pub/gnu/global/
eg: wget https://ftp.gnu.org/pub/gnu/global/global-6.6.8.tar.gz

4 unpack and install the gtags
./configure
or If you are not going to use gtags-cscope, please try ./configure --disable-gtagscscope
make
sudo make install

5 use the gtags
gtags -v ./
